title: Can't connect new bluetooth earbuds
content:
I have a Pixel XL.
I've got new bluetooth earbuds last day.
I tried to pairing, but my phone can't find it.
There is no list.
I tried to connect to other devices as other phones, tablet, laptop... other all devices can connect.
Only my Pixel XL can't connect it, but nothing.
I tried to restarted the phone several times.
The earbuds doesn't have NFC, only bluetooth.
But Pixel doesn't show me the pairing list.
What can I have to for?
